Module org.example.camping2
Package org.example.camping2.dto

Class AcompañanteId

java.lang.Object
org.example.camping2.dto.AcompañanteId
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable
@Embeddable public class AcompañanteId extends Object implements Serializable
Composite primary key for the `Acompañante` entity. This class represents a unique identifier for a companion in the reservation system, composed of the companion ID, client ID, and reservation ID. It implements `Serializable` to be used as an embedded primary key in the `Acompañante` entity.
Since:
31/01/2025
Version:
1.0.0
Author:
Andrews Dos Ramos
